description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Instructional: Master the Catch ' from the channel Aquil Abdullah.
The workout falls under Warm-up/Warm-up.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Learn what the catch position is from Aquil and how to properly position your body at the catch. 

Max rhythm: 26, Format: Technique ...
